@startuml Onboarding Worker Flow (Simplified)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam BoxPadding 20

title Onboarding Auto-Generation Worker Flow (Simplified)\nTarget: 150 Leads → 450 Emails (3-touch sequence)

box "Client" #LightBlue
  actor User
  participant Frontend
end box

box "API Layer" #LightGreen
  participant "Onboarding\nAPI" as API
  participant "SSE\nStream" as SSE
end box

box "Background Processing" #LightYellow
  participant "BullMQ\nQueue" as Queue
  participant "Onboarding\nWorker" as Worker
end box

box "Data Sources" #LightCoral
  participant "BigQuery" as BQ
  participant "Hunter.io" as Hunter
  participant "AI (Gemini)" as AI
end box

box "Storage" #LightGray
  database PostgreSQL as DB
  database Redis
end box

== 1. Job Initialization ==

User -> Frontend: Submit survey
Frontend -> API: POST /start-discovery\n(industry, country, target)
API -> Queue: Add job\n(onboarding-{workspaceId})
Queue -> Redis: Store checkpoint
API --> Frontend: { jobId }
Frontend -> SSE: Subscribe to progress
activate SSE
SSE --> Frontend: Connected ✓

== 2. Phase: Discovery (150 Leads) ==

Queue -> Worker: Execute job
activate Worker
Worker -> Redis: Load checkpoint

Worker -> AI: Get B2B target industries
AI --> Worker: [Industry1, Industry2, ...]

loop 3 iterations × 1-3 industries
  Worker -> BQ: Search companies (100/query)
  BQ --> Worker: Company data

  loop For each company
    alt Domain duplicate
      Worker -> Worker: ⊗ Skip duplicate
    else Employee count > 5000
      Worker -> Worker: ⊗ Skip large company\n(target SMBs)
    else Valid company
      Worker -> Worker: Add to enrichment batch
    end
  end

  loop Batches of 30
    Worker -> Hunter: Get emails (Domain Search)
    Hunter --> Worker: contact@company.com
    Worker -> AI: Enrich company data
    AI --> Worker: Business type, description
    Worker -> DB: Save leads
    Worker -> SSE: Progress update
    SSE --> Frontend: X/150 leads found

    alt >= 150 leads
      Worker -> Worker: ✓ Target reached
    end
  end
end

alt < 150 leads after BigQuery
  Worker -> SSE: Starting Hunter.io fallback
  SSE --> Frontend: Searching more leads...

  Worker -> AI: Generate Hunter.io query
  AI --> Worker: Search params

  loop Paginate until 150
    Worker -> Hunter: Lead Discovery API
    Hunter --> Worker: Companies list

    loop For each company
      alt Domain already in processedWebsites
        Worker -> Worker: ⊗ Skip duplicate
      else emailsCount > 100
        Worker -> Worker: ⊗ Skip large company\n(>100 emails = proxy for big company)
      else Valid company
        Worker -> Hunter: Domain Search API
        Hunter --> Worker: Generic email
        Worker -> DB: Save lead\n(source: hunterio-discover)
        Worker -> Worker: Add domain to processedWebsites
      end
    end
  end
end

Worker -> Redis: ✓ Checkpoint (150 leads)
Worker -> SSE: Discovery complete
SSE --> Frontend: 150 leads found ✓

== 3. Phase: Group & Templates ==

Worker -> DB: Create customer group\n"Demo Lead Group"
Worker -> DB: Add 150 leads to group
Worker -> Redis: ✓ Checkpoint (groupId)
Worker -> SSE: Group created
SSE --> Frontend: Group ready ✓

loop 3 email templates
  Worker -> AI: Generate template\n(Introduction/Follow-up 1/Follow-up 2)
  AI --> Worker: {subject, body}
  Worker -> Redis: ✓ Cache template
  Worker -> SSE: Template X/3 ready
  SSE --> Frontend: Templates: X/3
end

Worker -> SSE: Templates complete
SSE --> Frontend: 3 templates ready ✓

== 4. Phase: Sequence & Previews ==

Worker -> DB: Create sequence\n"Demo Email Sequence"
Worker -> DB: Create 3 steps\n(Day 0, 1, 2 delays)
Worker -> Redis: ✓ Checkpoint (sequenceId)
Worker -> SSE: Sequence ready
SSE --> Frontend: Sequence created ✓

Worker -> DB: Get/create email account
loop 150 leads × 3 steps = 450 emails
  Worker -> Worker: Replace variables\n{{company}}, {{name}}
  Worker -> DB: Insert preview email\n(status: draft)

  alt Every 10 emails
    Worker -> SSE: Progress X/450
    SSE --> Frontend: Generated X/450 emails
  end
end

Worker -> SSE: Previews complete
SSE --> Frontend: 450 emails ready ✓

== 5. Complete ==

Worker -> DB: Update onboarding_progress\n(currentStep: 2)
Worker -> Redis: ✓ Final checkpoint
Worker -> SSE: Complete!
SSE --> Frontend: Onboarding done ✓
deactivate SSE
deactivate Worker

Frontend -> User: ✅ Success!\n150 leads, 450 emails

== Error Recovery ==

note over Worker, Redis
  **Checkpoint Resume:**
  - Job fails → saves error
  - Retry with exponential backoff
  - Resumes from last phase
  - Skips completed work
end note

@enduml
